trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> class initiates a search operation.
trans-unit.target: O classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> inicia uma operação de pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: This constructor creates an empty request.
trans-unit.target: Este construtor cria uma solicitação vazia.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the object at which to start the search.
trans-unit.target: O nome diferenciado do objeto no qual iniciar a pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: An LDAP search filter.
trans-unit.target: Um filtro de pesquisa LDAP.

trans-unit.source: One of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope" /> that specifies the search scope.
trans-unit.target: Um dos valores de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope" /> que especifica o escopo da pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: An array that contains the requested attributes in the result set.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz que contém os atributos solicitados no conjunto de resultados.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope,System.String[])" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> class using the specified name, search filter, scope, and attributes.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope,System.String[])" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> usando o nome, filtro de pesquisa, escopo e atributos especificados.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the object for which to search.
trans-unit.target: O nome diferenciado do objeto para o qual pesquisar.

trans-unit.source: A DSML v2 search filter.
trans-unit.target: Um filtro de pesquisa DSML v2.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope" /> value that specifies the search scope.
trans-unit.target: Um valor <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope" /> que especifica o escopo da pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope" />.
trans-unit.target: O valor padrão é <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope" />.

trans-unit.source: An array that contains the requested attributes in the result set.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz que contém os atributos solicitados no conjunto de resultados.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.Xml.XmlDocument,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope,System.String[])" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> class using the specified name, search filter, scope, and attributes.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.Xml.XmlDocument,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchScope,System.String[])" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest" /> usando o nome, filtro de pesquisa, escopo e atributos especificados.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Aliases" /> property contains one of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DereferenceAlias" /> that specifies the dereference alias behavior.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Aliases" /> contém um dos valores de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DereferenceAlias" /> que especifica o comportamento de alias de desreferenciação.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DereferenceAlias" /> value that specifies the dereference alias behavior.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DereferenceAlias" /> valor que especifica o comportamento de alias desreferenciamento.

trans-unit.source: The value is not a member of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DereferenceAlias" />.
trans-unit.target: O valor não é um membro de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DereferenceAlias" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Attributes" /> property contains the attributes of the requested object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Attributes" /> contém os atributos do objeto solicitado.

trans-unit.source: The attributes of the requested object.
trans-unit.target: Os atributos do objeto solicitado.

trans-unit.source: Set this property to <see langword="null" /> to retrieve all attributes.
trans-unit.target: Defina essa propriedade como <see langword="null" /> para recuperar todos os atributos.

trans-unit.source: One of the strings in <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> object is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Uma das cadeias de caracteres no objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.DistinguishedName" /> property contains the distinguished name of the requested object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.DistinguishedName" /> contém o nome diferenciado do objeto solicitado.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the requested object.
trans-unit.target: O nome distinto do objeto solicitado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Filter" /> property contains the search filter.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Filter" /> contém o filtro de pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The search filter.
trans-unit.target: O filtro de pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: If the value is a string, this property is an LDAP search filter.
trans-unit.target: Se o valor for uma cadeia de caracteres, essa propriedade será um filtro de pesquisa LDAP.

trans-unit.source: If the value is an XML document, the property is a DSML v2 search filter.
trans-unit.target: Se o valor for um documento XML, a propriedade será um filtro de pesquisa DSML v2.

trans-unit.source: Any other type throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: Qualquer outro tipo gera uma exceção.

trans-unit.source: The value is not a string or an XML document.
trans-unit.target: O valor não é uma cadeia de caracteres nem um documento XML.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Scope" /> property contains one of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope" /> that specifies the scope of the search.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.Scope" /> contém um dos valores de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope" /> que especifica o escopo da pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: One of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope" /> that specifies the scope of the search.
trans-unit.target: Um dos valores de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope" /> que especifica o escopo da pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The value is not a member of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope" />.
trans-unit.target: O valor não é um membro de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.SizeLimit" /> property contains the maximum number of objects returned in the search request.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.SizeLimit" /> contém o número máximo de objetos retornados na solicitação de pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The maximum number of objects returned in the search request.
trans-unit.target: O número máximo de objetos retornados na solicitação de pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The value is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: O valor é menor que zero.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.TimeLimit" /> property contains a <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> object that specifies the time span allowed, if the server processes the search request.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.TimeLimit" /> contém um objeto <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> que, se o servidor processa a solicitação de pesquisa, especifica o período de tempo permitido.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> object that specifies the time span allowed, if the server processes the search request.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.TimeSpan" /> objeto que especifica o período de tempo permitido, se o servidor processa a solicitação de pesquisa.

trans-unit.source: The value is less than <see cref="F:System.TimeSpan.Zero" />.
trans-unit.target: O valor é menor que <see cref="F:System.TimeSpan.Zero" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.ToXmlNode(System.Xml.XmlDocument)" /> method creates an XML node from the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.ToXmlNode(System.Xml.XmlDocument)" /> cria um nó XML com base no objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The resulting <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O tipo do objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> resultante.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.TypesOnly" /> property specifies whether the search returns only the attribute names and not the attribute values.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchRequest.TypesOnly" /> especifica se a pesquisa retorna somente os nomes de atributo e não os valores de atributo.

trans-unit.source: If this property is <see langword="true" />, the search returns only the attribute names.
trans-unit.target: Se essa propriedade for <see langword="true" />, a pesquisa retorna somente os nomes de atributo.

trans-unit.source: If this property is <see langword="false" />, the search returns both the attribute names and values.
trans-unit.target: Se essa propriedade for <see langword="false" />, a pesquisa retorna os valores e nomes de atributo.
